==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Mercurous
<hw>Mer*cu"rous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>Of, pertaining to, or derived from, mercury; containing mercury; --
said of those compounds of mercury in which it is present in its highest
proportion.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Mercurous chloride</b></col>. <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <cd>See
<er>Calomel</er>.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mercury</ent>⟦br⟧
